attachments.ocrText: May be an image of text that says 'ANMA ECLIPTICA 23 NOVEMBER•BERLIN BERLIN NOVEMBER I'm preparing here in Berlin part art, part inner journey. The idea is that every artist, dancer, or creator carries shadow inside, and that shadow actually hides their greatest light. During Anima Ecliptica, we use music, voice-and movement to transform that inner tension into pure expression- to let soul crea- te again. It's inspired by ancient wisdom schools, but it's made for our time real, artistic, human. This day will feature meditation and ritual work aligned with the astrological significance of the date.'

***CASTING FOR NATIVITY! THE MUSICAL***

Looking for musical theatre performers who are not doing panto but would still love to do a show this Christmas!!

We are producing a charity production of NATIVITY! THE MUSICAL here in Romford

We are looking for....

GORDON SHAKESPEARE (Male - playing age 30-45) Hugely competitive teacher at Oakmoor Prep School. Bari/Tenor vocals

LORD MAYOR / ENSEMBLE (Male - playing age 35-60)

MISS RYE / ENSEMBLE (Female - playing age 23-50)

THE CRITIC / ENSEMBLE (Any Gender - playing age 25-60)

HOLLYWOOD PRODUCER / ENSEMBLE (Any Gender - playing age 25-60)

Show runs 4-23 Dec 2025

Venue: Brookside Theatre Romford

Production: Charity musical

Rehearsals: Monday - Thursday daytimes / evenings by schedule

Remuneration: Flat Fee

Please PM for more info or email harri@brooksidetheatre.com

items.text:
I am a 2nd year film production student at UCA in Farnham, Surrey.

We are currently in the process of trying to find extras for our film that we are shooting in sugar shack (the old pop world) in Portsmouth. Due to the brief we can only have people who are 18+ the dates we will be needing you are the 17th and 19th of November 9am-5pm, dress code will be club attire. As we are only students and have a very limited budget we won’t be able to pay you for this role but we will provide catering, as well as this you will be mentioned in the credits of the film and this will be submitted to film festivals. If you have any questions or are interested please email me via - maddiewest2006@icloud.com or private message me alternatively you can find me on instagram filmsbymads06.

Thank you.

topComments.text: So happy to pay for festivals but not cast or crew?
Avoid, they have no interest in paying for people's time, only fame.

message.text:
Vor einigen Tagen habe ich im Netz einige Beiträge gesehen von Menschen auf der Straße. Sie wurden interviewt,  sind nach Herkunft, Perspektiven und mehr weiter gefragt worden. Das hat mich sehr aufgewühlt. Heute nach einer langen Studio Session habe ich mich gefragt warum ich so einen Song geschrieben habe? 
Mit“HINTER DEN BERGEN“ ist ein neues Werk für das Projekt SONNENFEUER entstanden.

🔥 Kostenloses Gesangs-Webinar, am Do., den 20.11.25 um 18:30 Uhr.🔥

Wenn du schon immer davon geträumt hast, deine Stimme zum Klingen zu bringen, dann habe ich genau das Richtige für dich! Melde dich jetzt zu meinem kostenlosen Webinar an und lerne mich persönlich kennen. 🌟

Sei dabei, stelle mir Fragen und entdecke die wunderbare Welt des Singens! 💫 Melde dich jetzt an! Den Link zum kostenfreien Webinar findest Du oben in meinem Profil oder hier: https://singasong-behappy.de/webinar/ 

Sing a Song-Be Happy! 
Ich freue mich auf dich,
Deine Bernadette 🎶

sharedPost.text:
🌴 POLEĆ ZE MNĄ NA ZANZIBAR! 🌴

W marcu 2026 ruszamy na 10 dni w raju – słońce, ocean, najlepsze plaże i pełen chill!
To nie będzie zwykła wycieczka, tylko przygoda życia: rejsy, lokalne smaki, wspólne imprezy, warsztaty i zachody słońca jak z pocztówki 🌅

Z nami leci też prywatny fotograf, więc wrócisz nie tylko z opalenizną, ale i zdjęciami, których wszyscy będą zazdrościć 📸

A dla pierwszych 5 osób – specjalna zniżka! 🔥

Zanzibar znam jak własną kieszeń – mieszkałem tam kilka miesięcy podczas nagrań Hotelu Paradise, więc pokażę Wam miejsca, o których nie piszą w przewodnikach 🌊

👉 Po więcej informacji i pełną ofertę napisz do mnie na PRIV! Liczba miejsc ograniczona – nie przegap tej przygody! ✈️

ODNAJDZ SPOKOJ, KIERUNEK SIEBIE ZOBACZ NOWĄ PERŚPEKTYWĘ NA ŻYCIE! WARSZTATY 1:1 PROFESJONALNE ZDJECIA Z PODRÓŻY! POGROMCY WYLOT: WYLOT:02.03-12.03.2026 02.03 12.03.2026 CENA: 2500 USD LOTY PODRÓZN'

items.text:
**Zapraszamy na plan!**

**Góra Kalwaria 24.11**

Ogłaszamy zdjęcia próbne do krótkometrażowego filmu fabularnego. To kluczowy etap przygotowań do większego projektu, który będzie realizowany w 2026 roku.

Będziemy pracować ze storyboardem: ćwiczyć sceny aktorskie - głównie monologi – co stanowi ciekawe wyzwanie i daje możliwość sprawdzenia swoich umiejętności.

## **POSZUKUJEMY DWÓCH RÓL:**
* Aktorka w wieku: **21-28 lat**
* Aktorka w wieku: **28-40 lat**
## **WYMAGANIA:**
* Naturalna uroda, szczupła sylwetka.
* Mile widziane dłuższe włosy.
* Doświadczenie aktorskie/filmowe mile widziane, ale jeśli masz pasję do kina i po prostu "czujesz" kamerę – również serdecznie zapraszamy!
## **WARUNKI:**
* **STAWKA:** 200 zł
* **CZAS PRACY:** ok. 5-6 godzin
* **LOKALIZACJA:** Góra Kalwaria
* **TERMIN:** Wstępnie 24 listopada (piątek) – termin jest elastyczny, możemy dopasować inny dzień.
* Możliwość dalszej współpracy przy kolejnych projektach.
## **JAK SIĘ ZGŁOSIĆ?**

Zgłoszenia prosimy wysyłać **WYŁĄCZNIE przez wiadomość prywatną (Messenger/Facebook)**. Chcemy mieć wszystko w jednym miejscu, co bardzo ułatwi nam pracę.

**Prosimy o kompletne zgłoszenie zawierające:**
1. Kilka aktualnych zdjęć (wyraźna twarz + cała sylwetka).
2. **Jedno zdjęcie twarzy bez makijażu.**
3. Informacje: Wiek, wzrost, miejsce zamieszkania.

**WAŻNE:** Prosimy **nie zamieszczać zgłoszeń w komentarzach** pod postem! Zgłoszenia wysłane w ten sposób nie będą brane pod uwagę.

**Organizator:**

https://karolalmert.com/film-studio/

Zapraszamy!

Hello again, I am looking for a backup actress for my project 'The Haven Institute' I am looking for a female, aged 21-23. The actress HAS to be based in Swansea as I am based in Swansea. The project is unpaid. This is a backup as I haven't had anything from the person already chosen to play the role of Iris Marsh. Currently in terms of filming I will send the script over and have the actress film in their own environment. 

Please email me at Thehollowreturn@outlook.com

In person filming is hoping to take place in the new year once I have more actors involved

items.text:
## **CASTING CALL – “Tale of Two” (Short Film)**

**Logline:**
*“Tale of Two”* is a portrait short film about women’s strength, focusing on our shared experiences rather than our differences. Through small, intimate scenes, we witness key moments in the lives of two women as they navigate hardship, love, and resilience in parallel journeys.

**Production Details:**
* **Location:** Downtown Vancouver
* **Shoot Dates:** 1-3 days – end of January
* **Format:** MOS (no sync sound) – performances will rely heavily on expressive, facial acting
* **Union Status:** Non-Union / Volunteer Passion Project
* **Compensation:** Volunteer basis with **great meals, greater company, and IMDb credit**.
Select roles (requiring multiple full days) will receive a **small honorarium**.

**To Submit:**
Please send your **headshot and CV/demo reel**, which **role** you’re applying for and a **self-tape** with the attached actions **taleoftwofilm@gmail.com**.
Include a **slate** with your **name, age, height,** and any **unavailable dates**.
**Submission Deadline:** *November 25th at midnight.*

Casting Call!

*Starchild* is a sci-fi drama that follows the story of two scientists, Vanessa and Tanner as they take separate paths to deal with their grief. Vanessa through faith, and Tanner through science. It's not until they discover the origins of life itself, that they reconcile to start a family of their own. 

The film is heartfelt, honest, and powerful.

Please send resume, headshot, and (if applicable) demo reel to starchildcasting@gmail.com

Die WSI Agentur sucht aktuell für folgende Rollen Darsteller!

Alle weiteren Details finden Sie nachfolgend:

Gesuchte Rolle: Pärchen 

- einen Mann (30-45)

- eine Dame  (30-45)

Was wird gedreht/produziert?

•  Social Media Content - Kurzvideos (bis ca. 30 Sekunden mit Sprechrollen) und Bilder (div. Motive)

Aufnahmeort: Leibnitz 

Zeitraum: am 20.11.2025

Falls wegen Schlechtwetter abgesagt werden muss gibt es einen Ersatztermin: 24.11.2025 oder 27.11.2025 

Gage: - Gagenvorstellung des Darstellers für einen halben Drehtag für die ausgeschriebene Rolle

Erfahrung benötigt:

•  Erste Produktionserfahrung von Vorteil

•  Natürlich freuen wir uns auch über Bewerbungen von Laiendarstellern

Die Bewerbung soll bitte unbedingt enthalten:

•  Aktuelle Bilder - min. 3 unterschiedliche Bilder (Polas - Handyfotos)

•  Kurzes Vorstellungsvideo

•  Kontaktdaten: Name, Geburtsdatum, Telefonnummer, Meldeadresse

•  Gagenvorstellung für einen halben Drehtag für die ausgeschriebene Rolle

Wir freuen uns über Ihre Bewerbung an casting@weshootit.com.

Wir bedanken uns und wünschen schöne Grüße aus Graz!

KRAKÓW, poszukiwana dziewczynka 6-8 lat

Do jednej sceny w filmie krótkometrażowym z wątkiem AI realizowanej w Krakowie 23 listopada (niedziela) szukamy dziewczynki w wieku 6-8 lat z talentem aktorskim. Film powstaje w ramach świetlicy filmowej, ale planujemy dla niego również dystrybucję festiwalową. Rodziców zapraszamy do wysłania maila ze zdjęciem i jeśli to możliwe z krótkim nagraniem video, imieniem i nazwiskiem, wiekiem oraz wzrostem na adres marzena.casting@gmail.com. Oferta non-profit. Czas trwania planu 2-3 h. Miejsce: centrum Krakowa okolica Ronda Grzegórzeckiego.

sharedPost.text:
🌴 POLEĆ ZE MNĄ NA ZANZIBAR! 🌴

W marcu 2026 ruszamy na 10 dni w raju – słońce, ocean, najlepsze plaże i pełen chill!
To nie będzie zwykła wycieczka, tylko przygoda życia: rejsy, lokalne smaki, wspólne imprezy, warsztaty i zachody słońca jak z pocztówki 🌅

Z nami leci też prywatny fotograf, więc wrócisz nie tylko z opalenizną, ale i zdjęciami, których wszyscy będą zazdrościć 📸

A dla pierwszych 5 osób – specjalna zniżka! 🔥

Zanzibar znam jak własną kieszeń – mieszkałem tam kilka miesięcy podczas nagrań Hotelu Paradise, więc pokażę Wam miejsca, o których nie piszą w przewodnikach 🌊

👉 Po więcej informacji i pełną ofertę napisz do mnie na PRIV! Liczba miejsc ograniczona – nie przegap tej przygody! ✈️

items.text:
Probably a weird question, I wrote a screenplay for a pilot and I was wondering if anyone had any advice about the next steps on getting it in the hands of someone that could produce it. I just need a chance to submit it and see where it goes. Does anyone have any experience with this. 

Long time writer, first time writing a pilot.

topComments.text:
Every pilot that I’ve worked on has had financial investments in order to produce at least the teaser. If not the full episode.

Even when Elijah would wanted the role of Frodo and Lord of the rings, he just put together a teaser trailer with himself in it to sell the idea that’s essentially what a pilot is 

Trying to sell the idea of a story, not necessarily the production company that puts it together ￼
Start posting for the people you need .. editing.. actors,directors.youll get people that want to be a part of it and help

❄️🌟 **Bliv frivillig statist i SNEDRONNINGEN 2026!** 🌟❄️- **CASTING** i Aarhus.

Drømmer du om at stå på scenen foran 3000 publikummer og være en del af Nordens største udendørs forestilling? - Nu har du chancen! 💫

Vi i Frivilligorganisationen ReThinker i samarbejde med Det Kongelige Teater inviterer til **casting den 20. og 21. januar 2026** – og du kan blive en del af H.C. Andersens magiske univers, når Moesgaards bakke forvandles til et isglitrende eventyr. ✨

👉 Tilmeld dig casting via linket i kommentarfeltet

 

Som frivillig statist får du nye venner, uforglemmelige oplevelser og suget i maven, når tæppet går op. ❤️

 

Periode:

**Prøveperioden** er fra 20. april - 19. maj

**Spilleperioden** er fra 20. maj - 27. juni.

 

👀 Er du nysgerrig?
Kom til **informationsmøde torsdag den 27. november kl. 19.00 i Aarhus**, og hør mere om rollerne, fællesskabet og hvordan du tilmelder dig casting.

 

👉 Se prøve- og spilleplan, og tilmeld dig informationsmøde eller CASTING via linket i kommentarfeltet.

 

*Foto af: Camilla Winther*

Kvindelige skuespillere søges (Ulønnet)

Louises vaskemaskine er gået i stykker, og hun ender på et lokalt vaskeri, hvor hun – lidt modvilligt – må ringe til sin gamle ven Andrea for hjælp.
Mens de sidder og sorterer tøjet, falder en gammel vietnamesisk mønt ud af en bukselomme. Den vækker minder fra en fælles rejse nogle år forinden – og starter en samtale om, hvad der egentlig skete dengang, og hvordan det stadig præger deres relation.

Vi holder casting i løbet af ugen, og den næste. I Århus. Vi regner med at filme et par dage i uge 48 i Århus.

I kan kontakte mig på hjaltepotemkin@gmail.com

✨ **BIG NEWS! NATIONAL PAGEANTS 2026** ✨

Get ready to sparkle, shine, and take the stage — because the next **National Pageants** are officially happening on **27 & 28 February 2026** at the breathtaking **Excalibur Boutique Hotel in Rustenburg!** 👑🌸

We can’t wait to celebrate another incredible weekend filled with **beauty, confidence, and empowerment** — where dreams come alive and ambassadors are born. 💫

Before we step into a new season of inspiration, we’d love to celebrate our amazing **2024 National Ambassadors** who continue to make us proud:
🌷 *Little Miss Petite South Africa 2024* – **Layla Steyn**
🌼 *Little Miss South Africa 2024* – **Anke Strydom**
🌸 *Miss Pre-Teen International South Africa 2024* – **Sky Njoko**
🌺 *Miss Teen South Africa 2024* – **Chriské Schwirzer**

Thank you for shining your light and inspiring the next generation of young women across South Africa! 💖

📍 **Venue:** Excalibur Boutique Hotel, Rustenburg
🌐 **Website:** [www.sacopa.co.za](http://www.sacopa.co.za)

# **CASTING CALL FOR:**
# **ACTORS, VOICE ACTORS, SINGERS/VOCALISTS**
## 
# *' he lives here. '*

MANCHESTER BASED ONLY 

From writer/director/producer Jacob James Ward 

Watch my showreel here:

[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gIponbMURSU](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gIponbMURSU)

'he lives here.'

A sleepless corporate worker is forced to confront the monstrous embodiment of their childhood trauma during a terrifying sleep paralysis episode

A new gothic-noir, psychological thriller!

This project is deeply rooted in experimental film, with roles dominantly demanding body-performance with smaller amounts of spoken dialogue. 

This could be a good fit for those looking to get into experimental film with interests in deep character development/immersion within the horror/thriller genres! 

CASTING FOR 2 MAIN ROLES, VOICE ACTORS & VOCALISTS

BENNY

Male presenting, playing age 20-30

Benny, a reclusive loner caught between a draining job and worsening sleep paralysis partially due to unresolved trauma from his estranged father, battles his paranoia in an empty house

THE FIGURE 

Male presenting, playing age 20-30 

A manifestation of his deepest fears, the figure appears to Benny one evening in frightening hallucinations

VOICE ACTORS

Any age, but with a focus on more mature voices (40+) 

VOCALIST

To help in making the score of the film. Feminine-leaning vocals rooted in dreamy soundscapes and soft spoken word. Inspo: Phoebe Bridgers, Agnes Obel, Ethel Cain

Filming on dates in December (depending on actor availability) 

UNPAID STUDENT FILM 

MANCHESTER BASED ONLY 

Please reach out via this Facebook page or email at jacobward044@gmail.com 

to express interest and find out more info!

Much love 

X

items.text:
Casting Call for Short 10-15 minutes called Repossession 

This is a  darkly comic short about ambition, fame, and the unexpected horrors lurking behind a routine job.

Casting call for the characters 
Kyle
 A seasoned presenter clinging to relevance in a changing media landscape. Desperate for a comeback, he takes one last job—blinded by ambition, even when the warning signs turn supernatural.
 Playing Age: Early 30s to mid 40s
 Ethnicity: Any
 Gender: Male
Spencer
 Kyle’s loyal second-in-command, tasked with shaping the show’s content. Often dragged into eerie locations, Spencer must confront whether he’s valued as a partner—or just a pawn.
 Playing Age: Mid 20s to Mid 30s
 Ethnicity: Any
 Gender: Male
Carla Curses
 A flashy social media psychic with a massive following and a hunger for viral fame. Her pursuit of a haunted object leads to possession—transforming her into something savage and inhuman.
 Playing Age: 20s to 30s
 Ethnicity: Any
 Gender: Female
Frank
Carla’s trusted cameraman, now shattered by the night’s horrors. Haunted and fragile, his trauma slowly pulls him into the house’s darkness.
Playing Age: 30s to 40s
Ethnicity: Any
Physicality: Tall and lanky
Gender: Male

Filming will take place in the Liverpool/Merseyside area, United Kingdom. Looking to film middle to end of January 2026 
Please apply only if you're based locally.
For more details, contact: houndsoftheroundtable@gmail.com

Please note we do not reply to comments or direct Facebook messages. Thank you!

 Ethnicity: Any
 Gender: Female
Frank
Carla’s trusted cameraman, now shattered by the night’s horrors. Haunted and fragile, his trauma slowly pulls him into the house’s darkness.
Playing Age: 30s to 40s
Ethnicity: Any
Physicality: Tall and lanky
Gender: Male

Filming will take place in the Liverpool/Merseyside area, United Kingdom. Looking to film middle to end of January 2026 
Please apply only if you're based locally.
For more details, contact: houndsoftheroundtable@gmail.com

Please note we do not reply to comments or direct Facebook messages. Thank you!

items.text:
—————CASTING CALL FOR **THE GREEN PASSPORT**—————

We are students of Budapest Metropolitan University and currently in our 3rd year on Film and Media bachelors. For our Diploma Film we are looking for actors in 2 main roles. 

LOGLINE OF THE FILM:

In a midst of chaos caused by losing her passport on the first day of the visit, the mom and the son rediscover their long gone connection and love for each other. And the trip ends and they have to say goodbye when they finally reconnect with each other.

Below you can find the important infos about the characters:

CHARACTER’S RACE
* South American
* South Asian

MARIA
* 50
* Nurse
* Overprotective, still distant
* Slightly closed minded
* Not expressive or vulnerable most of the time
* Caring but does not know how to 
* Kind
* Emotionally strong
* Ambitious
* From a working class family and saved up money to be in Europe
* Does not speak English well

ETHAN
* 20 - 27
* Lives in Europe
* Studies literature English
* Used to be sweet and naive but now more aware and mature
* Academically smart but not street smart 
* Gets overwhelmed easily 
* Anxious in stressful situations but manages to resolve them
* Expressive, shows emotions but not to the mum

ADDITIONAL INFO ABOUT THE PROJECT:
* This is a university film and our budget is very low, so this is an **UNPAID** work.
* The shooting most probably will happen in the 2nd part of April. 
* Before the shooting we will hold rehearsals (end March/ early April).
* The shooting will happen in the actors’ native language, but the process of the shooting and the communication during the shoot will be English, so English language skills **REQUIRED**.

If you are interested please send us headshots and previous works of yourself to [thegreenpassport.work@gmail.com](mailto:thegreenpassport.work@gmail.com).

items.text:
Pet-Friendly 1-Bedroom Apartment – Furnish It Your Way! 🐾 – Budapest 13th District (Újlipótváros)
📍 Katona József utca 21 – Super central, right by WestEnd Mall & Nyugati Station
📅 Available now | 12-month lease
💶 Rent: 300,000 HUF/month + utilities
💡 Common cost: 15,000 HUF/month
💰 2-month deposit

Looking for a comfy, flexible place in one of Budapest’s most loved neighborhoods? This 47 sqm ground-floor apartment is warm, modern, and pet-friendly — and the best part? You get to furnish it your way!

✨ Apartment Highlights:
• Large bedroom with elegant Italian furniture already in place 🇮🇹🛏️
• Separate kitchen – will be fully equipped soon (fridge included!) 🍳
• Living room? We’ll furnish it based on your needs – or bring your own style
• Electric fireplace for cozy vibes 🔥
• Two AC units (in the bedroom and kitchen) for heating & cooling ❄️🔥
• Spacious bathroom with washing machine
• Ground-floor unit – easy access
• Totally pet-friendly, so bring your furry friend along! 🐶🐱

Furnish your new home around your lifestyle – especially great if you want to make it your own (or already have some favorite pieces).

📲 Interested? Reach out to Matin for a viewing!
📞 +36 20 462 8117 (WhatsApp / Telegram)

Vor einigen Tagen habe ich im Netz einige Beiträge gesehen von Menschen auf der Straße. Sie wurden interviewt,  sind nach Herkunft, Perspektiven und mehr weiter gefragt worden. Das hat mich sehr aufgewühlt. Heute nach einer langen Studio Session habe ich mich gefragt warum ich so einen Song geschrieben habe? 
Mit“HINTER DEN BERGEN“ ist ein neues Werk für das Projekt SONNENFEUER entstanden.

Hi! 

I’m currently casting a well paid shoot for an alcohol brand

As it’s advertising for alcohol all cast legally need to be at least 25 (production will ask for id to prove this if shortlisted by client) however the concept for the project is quite youthful so max age should be 30. 

Casting Brief: 

Looking for European girls with coloured hair (think red, blue, pink, green, berry, purple) or happy to have their hair coloured for the shoot. 

Looking for European boys with facial hair (a moustache and/or beard - bonus if you have an interesting hair cut too) 

This is a London shoot so looking for London based people only. 

**Shoot Dates: **Thursday 27th + Friday 28th November

Talent to attend both shoot days in London on Location

Based on a 10 hour shoot day including an additional hour for lunch

**Fitting Date:** Monday 24th November, 1-2 hours in London (between 9am and 6pm)

**Talent Age: **All Talent to be over 25 and passport or ID needs to be provided at the time of shortlist to confirm this 

**Talent Rates:**

Talent Day Rates - £600 per person per day

Talent Usage* £5,000 per model

*Usage not guaranteed however all talent are shot in groups so this is very likely to be confirmed

**Talent Wardrobe:**

Talent will be required to bring a couple of outfits to the shoot which will be briefed by the wardrobe stylist

and either brought to the fitting or photographed before the shoot.

£50 per person (total not per day)

To submit please fill in this form : 

[https://airtable.com/apprDbNv50EdHz0RT/pagpszb0AEzQg5XCi/form](https://airtable.com/apprDbNv50EdHz0RT/pagpszb0AEzQg5XCi/form)

And, please upload your self tape here: [https://www.dropbox.com/request/s2OXkOWhOSaif9oUoaCR](https://www.dropbox.com/request/s2OXkOWhOSaif9oUoaCR)

The deadline is 10AM, Monday 17th November. 

No requests, no PM’s 

Thank you! 

www.unit-c.co

# **🎄Elf Work at Hertfordshire Zoo!🎄**

Hertfordshire Zoo is looking for jolly, enthusiastic, and festive individuals to bring the magic of Christmas to life this year at **Hertfordshire Zoo in Broxbourne, Hertfordshire.**

**What We’re Looking For:**
* A warm, friendly personality with plenty of festive spirit
* Confidence interacting with children and families
* Reliability and professionalism
* Previous performance or grotto experience (preferred but not essential)
* We have a mixture of performance elf and grotto elf work available

**When You’ll Work:**

The dates we are currently still looking for people are:
* 26th November (4:30pm-8:30pm)
* 29th November (9:30am-4:00pm)
* 30th November (9:00am-5:00pm)
* 6th December (9:00am-5:00pm)
* 7th December (9:00am-5:00pm)
* 13th December (9:00am-5:00pm)
* 24th December (9:00am-3:00pm)

**PLEASE NOTE** - You are not required to be available to work on all of these dates. Any availability is accepted.

**What We Offer:**
* A fun and rewarding role in a magical setting
* £14 per hour
* Full costume and training provided
* The chance to work at one of Hertfordshire's most loved attractions

If you would love to make Christmas unforgettable for our visitors, we’d love to hear from you.

Apply now by emailing **[entertainment@hertfordshirezoo.com](mailto:entertainment@hertfordshirezoo.com)**

items.text:
Hey everyone,
I’m Michael Uchenik, a film student, and this December (11–16.12) I’ll be shooting my graduation film in Berlin, a story that explores the connection between trauma, love, and the body.

The entire film takes place during a laid-back house chill party, a warm, vibrant space where something deeper quietly unfolds.
It tells the story of David, an Israeli man full of life on the outside but haunted by a trauma he can’t escape, and Leo, his German boyfriend who tries to love him hard enough to bring him back to the present.

It’s a film about the duality of what we show versus what we hide.
About love as an anchor, and how memories follow us even when we move far away.

I’m looking for open-minded people who feel comfortable in front of the camera and with their bodies to join as participants in the party scenes.
This is not a pornographic film, but a sensitive and artistic project that looks at intimacy and vulnerability in an honest way.

If this sounds interesting to you, here’s a link with more info.

https://forms.gle/ZZJw8THu6qSW6UoKA 

And please feel free to share it with anyone who might be a good fit 💫

Thank you so much,
Michael

items.text:
Casting Call – Lead Role “Lil Messias” in Bachelor Film Groupies (The Norwegian Film School) - Paid! 

We are casting for Groupies, an ambitious and visually striking bachelor film by a talented team of students at The Norwegian Film School.

The film explores the groupie phenomenon through a music film about a rapper and a fangirl spending one surreal night backstage. Blending realism, stylization, and surreal imagery, Groupies delves into themes of power, status, gender roles, and what it truly means to be human in a superficial, image-driven world.

Role: Lil Messias (“Lil Mess”) – Lead
Lil Messias is an internationally acclaimed rap artist.
On stage, he radiates confidence, sex appeal, and dominance — the perfect image of modern masculinity.
Beneath the surface, however, he battles growing anxiety and emptiness in a life fueled by drugs, violence, and meaningless sex. He is trapped in his own image and longs to be truly seen. (Age 20-30)

This role involves:
 • An intimate scene with the character Ninni.
A professional intimacy coordinator will be attached to ensure a safe, respectful, and transparent process.
 • A rap performance, including recording a song and potentially some choreography.
 • The creative team will also be developing a full artist brand around the character — an exciting opportunity to embody a complete on-screen persona.

Actors of all ethnicities and backgrounds are strongly encouraged to apply.

Production Details
 • Shooting period: Between January 20–30, 2025
 • Location: Norway
 • Compensation: According to Norwegian industry rates (Tariff)

Travel expenses will be covered. (Europe only)

If this sounds like something for you, please get in touch. Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.

Please send location, portrait and if you have: showreel and/or introduction tape.

Email: deteramalie@gmail.com

🎬 CALL FOR CREW & PARTICIPANTS – GRADUATION FILM IN BERLIN 🎬

Hey everyone!
I’m a film student shooting my graduation short film in Berlin (Dec 11–16).

🖤 The film is an intimate story about love tested by trauma, about how the body carries memory, and how, even in moments of joy, the past can suddenly surface.
 It all takes place during a chill house party, where music, emotion, and memory slowly start to blend.
🧩 Looking for crew:
* Production Manager / Coordinator

* Assistant Director (AD)

* Production Assistant (PA)

Preferably based in Berlin, with some set experience and a collaborative, creative spirit.
 This is a student film – expenses are covered, and the atmosphere is warm, artistic, and professional.

👉 If you’re interested or want more info, contact:
 📧 safeshore2025@gmail.com
💫 Also looking for participants / extras:

The film includes scenes from a relaxed house party setting.
 I’m looking for open-minded people who feel comfortable being filmed and with their bodies.
 ⚠️ This is not a pornographic project – it’s a sensitive, artistic exploration of intimacy, love, and memory.

👉 To apply or learn more:
 📄[ ](https://forms.gle/upDRMqiPHYRemdPU6)https://forms.gle/upDRMqiPHYRemdPU6

Please apply only if you're based locally.

Please note we do not reply to comments or direct Facebook messages. Thank you!

CASTING CALL FOR NEW PLAY!
--------------------------------

A New Comedic play by Zack Faulks, *Bulimia is My Roman Empire* follows a group of Servants as they attempt to assassinate the Emperor. They discover that power may not be all that they had once desired. Learning that their target is engaged in a number of self-destructive behaviours, our conspirators are forced to follow down a long rabbit hole of strange diets, machismo, and fascism should they want to prove that they deserve the right to rule. As a satire of manhood, ultimately no one’s happy with where they end up.

For more information check out the images below!

Deadline to submit is Nov. 29, 2025 at 12:00pm.

--------------------
Find us at www.greattrashproductions.ca

items.text:
Casting Call (Non-Union) for COUPLES - Paid

Looking for actors to play the role of clients in a simulated therapy session. The video clips will be used in an online training system for counselors and psychologists. The sessions include some scripted elements to prepare, and then some improv with prompts.

We are currently interested in filming with mature couples, queer couples, interracial couples, or throuples/polycules of various gender identity combinations. All ages, all gender expressions/identities, all ethnicities, and persons with disabilities are welcome. 

All experience levels with acting are welcome, including experienced actors with less experienced partners. We are committed to making this a respectful and safe process, with open communication and respect for boundaries.

Comfortable English fluency is required.

Immediate filming dates are November 14 to 18, based on actor availability, but more will occur in the future so please submit if you're interested at all.

Location is downtown Vancouver - Gastown. Pay is $90 CAD per performer, with the expectation of some prepared material, studio session duration: 1 hour

Please email phil@skillsetter.com with your headshot and resume, as well as some information about you and your partner, such as gender identities, age, cultural/racial backgrounds. If you've submitted for a past session, you're welcome to submit again. We do sometimes receive more submissions than we are able to respond to, but we do read them all, and we do save your submissions for future consideration.

items.text:
Exciting News !
I'm thrilled to share my book EDDIE'S BACK -- A gripping story that I believe would make a FANTASTIC MOVIE.

I've already WRITTEN AND COPYRIGHTED THE SCREENPLAY, so it's ready to go! Now, I'm reaching out to production companies, literary agents, film agents, and directors who might be interested in bringing this story to life on the big screen.

EDDIE'S BACK - May 1963, Eddie a popular teenager is intentionally hit by a car, which leaves him in a coma. It's 2025, Eddie wakes up. He is shocked and disappointed at what he sees. Until the ghost of JFK visits him and inspires him to make a difference.

Now Eddie 77 years young, realizes why he was kept alive and what he has to do.

However, a senior Senator with an agenda of his own is watching Eddie's every move and is prepared to stop his mission at any cost.

DREAM CAST (Just Imagining!)
#HarrisonFord - #CandyClark - #PaulLeMat - #RichardDreyfuss - #CharlesSDutton - #MarkWahlberg - #MatthewMcConaughey - #MargotRobbie - #RobertDeniro - #BradleyCooper - #TaylorSwift - #MorganFreeman - #NicolasCage - #GregKinnear - #AnneHathaway - #WillFerrell - #PatrickSchwarzenegger - #joancollins -#kellyopsal -#islacervelli - #JackHyde -#LaurenSanchez -#jeffbezos -#elonmusk -#JordonHudson -#parishilton 
DIRECTOR - #RonHoward

NO OFFICIAL TIES - JUST PUTTING IT OUT THERE AND HOPING TO GET EDDIE'S BACK INTO THE RIGHT HANDS!

TAGGING TOP AGENCIES:
#ImagineEntertainment - #IndependentArtistGroup - #WilliamMorrisEndeavor - #VerveTalentandLiteraryManagement - #TheWayneAgency - #CAA
And indie powerhouses like: #A24 - #AnnapurnaPictures - #PlanBEntertainment - #BlumhouseProductions - #KillerFilms - #Neon - #FilmNation - #BleeckerStreet - #ElaraPictures - #BigBeach

NO OFFICIAL TIES - Just putting it out there and hoping to get EDDIE'S BACK into THE RIGHT HANDS!

PRODUCTION COMPANIES I ADMIRE:
#SONYPICTURES - #WARNERBROSDISCOVERY - #IMAGEENTERTAINMENT - #WALTDISNEYPICTURES

PRODUCERS - I'd love to work with:
#MarkCiardi - #MattDamon - #MarkWahlberg - #WillFerrell - #TomHanks

NO OFFICIAL TIES - Just putting it out there and hoping to get EDDIE'S BACK into THE RIGHT HANDS!

#Eddie'sBack #BooktoFilm #Screenplayready #Filmadaptation #Moviepitch #Filmmakers #producers #directors #Independentfilm #IndieCinema #literaryAgents

WHAT IF EDDIE (HARPER) AND JOHN (MILLER) WERE FRIENDS IN 1963?

Let's make movie magic happen!

PEOPLE WILL COME!

They haven’t stepped foot in a movie theater in 40 years.
Not since the golden days of double features and balcony seats.
But one day, without even knowing why…
THEY GET IN THEIR CAR AND GO

Not for the stadium seating.
Not for the surround sound.
**But for something deeper. Something they’ve been missing.**

They walk into the lobby — wide-eyed, hearts open, like children.
The smell of popcorn. The hum of the projector.
A moment suspended in time.

They don’t blink when the clerk says, “Twenty dollars.
Because this isn’t a transaction — it’s a Homecoming.

They find their old seats… the very ones from their childhood.
And the screen lights up with a story that speaks to the soul.

**Eddie’s Back** isn’t just a movie.
It’s a bridge across generations.
A story that blends nostalgia, humor, and hope — with just enough magic to make you believe again.

They will laugh.
They will cry.
And most importantly…
**They will remember.**

Baby Boomers will come.
They will bring their children.
Their grandchildren.
And one day — their great-grandchildren.

Because *Eddie’s Back* reminds them of what was good…
**And what can still be good again.**

The one constant through all the years has been family films —
**Stories that bring us together.**

Oh yes — people will come.
Not because they need to… but because their hearts tell them to!
And when they do…
**They’ll thank you for bringing it to life.**

Now Eddie 77 years young, realizes why he was kept alive and what he has to do.

However, a senior Senator with an agenda of his own is watching Eddie's every move and is prepared to stop his mission at any cost.

DREAM CAST (Just Imagining!)
#HarrisonFord - #CandyClark - #PaulLeMat - #RichardDreyfuss - #CharlesSDutton - #MarkWahlberg - #MatthewMcConaughey - #MargotRobbie - #RobertDeniro - #BradleyCooper - #TaylorSwift - #MorganFreeman - #NicolasCage - #GregKinnear - #AnneHathaway - #WillFerrell - #PatrickSchwarzenegger - #joancollins -#kellyopsal -#islacervelli - #JackHyde -#LaurenSanchez -#jeffbezos -#elonmusk -#JordonHudson -#parishilton 
DIRECTOR - #RonHoward

NO OFFICIAL TIES - JUST PUTTING IT OUT THERE AND HOPING TO GET EDDIE'S BACK INTO THE RIGHT HANDS!

TAGGING TOP AGENCIES:
#ImagineEntertainment - #IndependentArtistGroup - #WilliamMorrisEndeavor - #VerveTalentandLiteraryManagement - #TheWayneAgency - #CAA
And indie powerhouses like: #A24 - #AnnapurnaPictures - #PlanBEntertainment - #BlumhouseProductions - #KillerFilms - #Neon - #FilmNation - #BleeckerStreet - #ElaraPictures - #BigBeach

NO OFFICIAL TIES - Just putting it out there and hoping to get EDDIE'S BACK into THE RIGHT HANDS!

PRODUCTION COMPANIES I ADMIRE:
#SONYPICTURES - #WARNERBROSDISCOVERY - #IMAGEENTERTAINMENT - #WALTDISNEYPICTURES

PRODUCERS - I'd love to work with:
#MarkCiardi - #MattDamon - #MarkWahlberg - #WillFerrell - #TomHanks

NO OFFICIAL TIES - Just putting it out there and hoping to get EDDIE'S BACK into THE RIGHT HANDS!

#Eddie'sBack #BooktoFilm #Screenplayready #Filmadaptation #Moviepitch #Filmmakers #producers #directors #Independentfilm #IndieCinema #literaryAgents

WHAT IF EDDIE (HARPER) AND JOHN (MILLER) WERE FRIENDS IN 1963?

Let's make movie magic happen!

PEOPLE WILL COME!

They haven’t stepped foot in a movie theater in 40 years.
Not since the golden days of double features and balcony seats.
But one day, without even knowing why…
THEY GET IN THEIR CAR AND GO

Not for the stadium seating.
Not for the surround sound.
**But for something deeper. Something they’ve been missing.**

They walk into the lobby — wide-eyed, hearts open, like children.
The smell of popcorn. The hum of the projector.
A moment suspended in time.

They don’t blink when the clerk says, “Twenty dollars.
Because this isn’t a transaction — it’s a Homecoming.

They find their old seats… the very ones from their childhood.
And the screen lights up with a story that speaks to the soul.

**Eddie’s Back** isn’t just a movie.
It’s a bridge across generations.
A story that blends nostalgia, humor, and hope — with just enough magic to make you believe again.

They will laugh.
They will cry.
And most importantly…
**They will remember.**

Baby Boomers will come.
They will bring their children.
Their grandchildren.
And one day — their great-grandchildren.

Because *Eddie’s Back* reminds them of what was good…
**And what can still be good again.**

The one constant through all the years has been family films —
**Stories that bring us together.**

Oh yes — people will come.
Not because they need to… but because their hearts tell them to!
And when they do…
**They’ll thank you for bringing it to life.**

Hello everyone,

I’m Emmanuel, a casting director and camera operator for an upcoming episode of our horror anthology series, Whispers Beyond. We are currently looking for actors to join us for our next shoot, taking place Monday 17th November to Friday 21st November in the London area.

Casting Roles
 • Lena — Lead (Female, 20–35)
 • Mrs. Bell — Supporting (Female, 25–55)
 • Tom — Supporting (Male, 25–50)
 • The Man — Supporting (Male, 25–50)
 • Paramedic(s) — Supporting (Any gender, 18+)
 • New Customer — Supporting (Any gender, 18+)

Project Summary

Whispers Beyond is an anthology series featuring five unsettling tales — a haunted mailbox, broken salt lines, a cursed candle vigil, a silent café guest, and a deadly lullaby — where rituals fail, shadows feed, and belief is the only thing keeping the darkness out.

Production Details
 • Dates: Monday 17th – Friday 21st November
 • Location: London area
 • Compensation: This is an unpaid role.

However, production will provide food and beverages on set, and if the episode performs well, there may be opportunities for compensation based on its success. (For the lead only). This project is a strong opportunity to collaborate with a reputable company, gain valuable on-set experience, and build your portfolio with high-quality material.

How to Apply

If you’re interested, please email: Hundofilms@gmail.com

Include the following in your application:
 • Name
 • Age
 • Photo
 • CV
 • Answers to the following questions:
 1. Are you available to work from Mon 17th – Fri 21st November?
 2. Are you comfortable with this being an unpaid role?

Thank you,
Emmanuel

topComments.text: You won't get anyone decent if it's unpaid unfortunately

items.text:
Still looking for volunteers for a Short film project who like to act in front of the camera.

The purpose of this short film is to create a new showreel for every actor and actress who’s gonna participate on it.

What's the movie supposed to be about?

A young man, once part of an underground operation supplying drugs to his boss, has since left the shady business to start a normal life.

Months later, he returns to the warehouse to surprise his former boss with a gift - but as he steps inside, he's struck by how much has changed. The familiar place now feels foreign, guarded, and tense.

After a brief, uneasy reunion, he runs into an old colleague, haunted by the past, does everything he can to avoid her before quickly leaving - closing the door on a life he's no longer part of.

Actors must be able to speak in English fluently!!

Open roles 

(Melly) Female, 18+

(Tasha) Female, 18+

(Maddie) Female, 18+

(Avi) Male, 45+

Extra 

Female & Male any ethnicity and 20+

For the spin

This will be shot in Cologne 

2 day between November 24-30 2025

If interested and available please send headshot to email officialemmanuelbenjamin@gmail.com

🎬 CASTING CALL – “EVIL GNOME”

In this campy slasher horror short, a young pair of dancers at an 80s tribute show sneak out (cheating on their partners) and are forced to face the consequences of their illicit actions. Trapped in a life or death game against a garden gnome possessed by an evil spirit , they must fight for their lives.

We’re casting for:
🧑‍🦱 1 Male Actor (19–25)
Role: Fabio a cocky, self-confident, dancer… drug dealer and aspiring footballer but a coward underneath his roadman exterior. Must have a strong London/ MLE accent. Costume will be provided. Must be available all day Monday 17th November 

📍 Filming Location: Egham, Surrey
🎥 Project: 6-minute short horror film 
📅 Shoot Date: Monday 17th November (11am–10pm)
🎞️ Self-tape or message Deadline: 11pm 15th November

If you’re passionate about fun, bold genre storytelling and love diving into energetic, expressive roles, we’d love to hear from you. This is an unpaid role for actors looking to gain experience or add to their portfolio.

📧 Please email arjanbains20@gmail.com for the audition pack, or send me a private message to learn more.

Please note this role is unpaid, but food and drink will be provided.

items.text:
Let’s be real for a moment… 📸

Headshots can sometimes feel like an extortionate expense - as a fellow actor, I get it. That’s why I keep my pricing fair, accessible, and realistic, without ever cutting corners on quality.

I see plenty of novice photographers grab a basic camera & kit lens then start offering “too good to be true” sessions in these groups for £30–£100 promising they’ll get you seen … but here’s the truth: Headshot photography is a specialist skill. Low end, inexpensive “quick fix” sessions might seem attractive at first but buy cheap, buy twice. 

Invest in a real headshot session with an award-winning photographer who brings experience, artistry, and skill to the table and get it right the first time. I’m a working actor too so I’m in your shoes and evolve with the times to provide the most updated, admired form of headshots.

Expect powerful, cinematic portraits that casting directors always notice. Clients regularly tell me their new headshots have led to more auditions, more callbacks and booked work - that’s exactly what I aim for.

I’ve had my fair share of awkward shoots; rushed sessions with cash grab cameramen who treated me like cattle, just another face passing through… I started doing this job to change that.
When you book with me, it’s never rushed. We’ll have a coffee, chat about your goals, play some tunes, and get you relaxed before the camera even comes out. My direction is creative and unorthodox - I’ll get you talking, laughing, and thinking, so we capture real moments that show who YOU are, not just what you look like.

The results speak for themselves - my clients have gone on to appear in major TV shows, films, high-end commercials, and even land roles on the West End. Your headshot is often your first impression - let’s make sure it’s unforgettable.

👉 View my portfolio: https://www.fandmmedia.co.uk/ryan-s-gallery

👉 Book a showreel scene, cinematic monologue recording, self tape sessions & more: https://www.fandmmedia.co.uk

🎭 On Spotlight? Enjoy £10 off any package!

Ryan 📸

F&M Media 🏆 Award-winning headshots that get you seen.

items.text:
**ULØNNET**

Vi er et hold fra Potemkin, Den Jyske Filmskole, der er i gang med vores afgangsprojekt

Vi søger en mand i spillealderen 18-23 til hovedrollen Milo

Kort om historien:
En ung mand med et spiralerende heroinmisbrug vender hjem til sin syge mor for første gang i månedsvis. Han kommer for at bede om penge - men ender som et stille opgør mellem kærlighed og skam. Vi ønsker ikke at lave en film som glorificerer stoffer, men om, hvordan det nedbryder de stærkeste relationer mellem mennesker.

Om rollen:
Milo er 23 og fanget i sit eget forfald. Bag afhængigheden gemmer sig en søn, der stadig elsker sin mor, men ikke længere kan bære at blive set af hende. Skylden, kærligheden og skammen eksisterer side om side i ham.
Rollen kræver en skuespiller med evnen til at udtrykke mere gennem stilhed end gennem ord - en fysisk og følelsesmæssig tilstedeværelse, hvor små reaktioner og blikke fortæller alt.

Praktisk:
Optagelserne finder sted i Aarhus den 24. og 25. november.
Der vil være fuld forplejning på settet, men vi vil ikke kunne betale køn, transport eller overnatning.

Hvis du er interesseret i at blive taget i betragtning til rollen, bedes du indsende et kort selftape af dummy teksten, der er vedhæftet i opslaget. Send det meget gerne til mailen nedenfor.

Vi håber, at projektet vækker din nysgerrighed - og at du har lyst til at tage del i fortællingen om Milo og hans mor.

Med venlig hilsen

Team “I Limbo”
Bastian Kapela
Producer, Potemkin – Den Jyske Potemkin Filmskole

bastiankapela@gmail.com

Milo er 23 og fanget i sit eget forfald. Bag afhængigheden gemmer sig en søn, der stadig elsker sin mor, men ikke længere kan bære at blive set af hende. Skylden, kærligheden og skammen eksisterer side om side i ham.
Rollen kræver en skuespiller med evnen til at udtrykke mere gennem stilhed end gennem ord - en fysisk og følelsesmæssig tilstedeværelse, hvor små reaktioner og blikke fortæller alt.

Praktisk:
Optagelserne finder sted i Aarhus den 24. og 25. november.
Der vil være fuld forplejning på settet, men vi vil ikke kunne betale køn, transport eller overnatning.

Hvis du er interesseret i at blive taget i betragtning til rollen, bedes du indsende et kort selftape af dummy teksten, der er vedhæftet i opslaget. Send det meget gerne til mailen nedenfor.

Vi håber, at projektet vækker din nysgerrighed - og at du har lyst til at tage del i fortællingen om Milo og hans mor.

Med venlig hilsen

Team “I Limbo”
Bastian Kapela
Producer, Potemkin – Den Jyske Potemkin Filmskole

bastiankapela@gmail.com

We are specifically looking for someone who can do card tricks to be the card dealer. A Doug Jones looking character but not necessarily. Could this be you? 

The shoot is set in a poker bar and the plot of the music video is a heist. The pay rate for the Dealer is £200 for the day. 

If you are interested - please email me ASAP with -recent headshot -full name -instagram handle -phone number -email

items.text:
It’s a wrap! Six Commercials with 50 Actors from MA to TX to RI and back to RI for 3 more this week!!  4 Picture cars in TX - RI!! Locations in RI!  

On Set Wrangler, Child Welfare Worker and Production Assistant!  

Catering and Crafty for 4 days! 

I have a new business: ACTORDASH - I don’t just cast ‘em! I deliver them to set!

I jumped in feet first starting in August 2025, and although we still have some administrative work to do; we are officially wrapped!

I am now on Holiday Break and will be gearing up for more filming in January 2026!

During this break I will be doing a massive Talent Scout starting in Rhode Island!

I know I can easily find everyone I need for our Massachusetts needs with a simple post! But, I’ve found it harder to find Actors in Rhode Island.

I am also planning a Karaoke Holiday Party for the first time since before Covid!  If you’d like to attend send an email to:

JodiPurdyCasting@gmail.com
Subj:  Holiday Party 2025

On another good note - my client is looking into signing a SAG Contract in 2026!  

But for the time being I will be casting Non-Union Actors and Real People to portray Doctors, Nurses, Medical Personnel and Patients from all walks of life living in Rhode Island.

Submit to:

JodiPurdyCasting@gmail.com
Subj: RI Resident NU Actor Real Person

Share:

Jodi Purdy (Name)
111-111-1111 (cell)
jodipurdycasting@gmail.com (email)
Weymouth, MA (location)

DO NOT TYPE (name, cell, email, location) ONLY YOUR INFO which I cut and paste!

Share:

Photos, videos, reels, links, resume, etc.

Celebrating tonight at the Orpheum Theater in Boston at a Dark Star Orchestra show with 3 of my besties!!

items.text:
Hi Everyone,
I am doing a 6 - minute documentary for my FMP that uses a core participants to explore how Cosplay is not a performance but entertainment, a way identity is expressed, shaped and performed.

It will document the participants' experience and highlight the experience from a first - time attendees, offering both a personal insight and broader perspective of UK Comic Con Culture. 

I need someone to Cosplay Catwoman and Harley Quinn at Bristol Comic Con on the 8th March 2026 at Ashton Gate Stadium. 

I wondered if you'd be interested?

I'd pay you £200.00

It's for my BA Hons Degree FMP and determines if I pass or fail.

I'd pay for your ticket and set the camera, it's from 10:30am - 16:00pm but you don’t have to stay the full day if you don't want to.

items.text:
🎬 **CASTING CALL – SOCIAL MEDIA CAMPAIGN (PAID)**
Casting multiple lifestyle roles for a social media video campaign shot in Johannesburg / Pretoria. All roles are paid. Seeking authentic talent with real, natural energy.

📅 **Production Date:** Late November 2025 (exact dates TBC)
⏳ **Submission Deadline:** ASAP
📍 **Location:** Johannesburg / Pretoria, South Africa
💰 **Pay:** Paid (rates discussed upon selection)
🏷 **Union Status:** Not Applicable
🎥 **Production Type:** Social Media Campaign

---

### **ROLES AVAILABLE**

🎭 **Braai Host (30–55, any gender)**
Warm, relatable South African energy. Must be comfortable prepping food, handling braai grid/tongs, and interacting naturally in a backyard scene.

🎣 **River Angler (28–50, any gender)**
Outdoorsy and calm. Should be comfortable mimicking fly-fishing movements and walking on uneven riverbank terrain.

🥾 **Hiker / Camper (20–35, any gender)**
Active, capable vibe. Will tie guylines, prep kindling, and perform light camp tasks in a scenic ridge/tent scene.

🚜 **Farmer / Farmhand (30–65, any gender)**
Authentic rural presence. Will appear in a field/shed scene doing light fence work, twine cutting, or walking crop rows.

---

### **SUBMISSION REQUIREMENTS**

📸 Headshot (natural light)
📷 Full-length photo
🖐 Hands close-ups (front & back)
🎥 20–30 sec video: State name, height, and languages spoken
🗣 Languages: English + any of Afrikaans, isiZulu, isiXhosa, or Sesotho (please indicate fluency)
📅 Confirm availability for late November
⚠️ Disclose any current commercial conflicts (e.g. food, outdoor, tools brands)

---

📩 **HOW TO APPLY**
Apply as a Talent PRO member via Actors and Extras with a **1-month FREE trial**:
🌐 [https://actorsandextras.com/casting-calls](https://actorsandextras.com/casting-calls)

Create your free profile and **GET NOTIFIED** of new roles in your area.
Join [www.actorsandextras.com](http://www.actorsandextras.com) today.

---

🔍 *This casting has been shared by Actors and Extras as a service to our talent directory members. We have received permission to share it and believe it to be legitimate. However, we strongly encourage all applicants to exercise due diligence and independently verify the details of the project before proceeding.*

#actorsandextras #actorlife #castingcall #southafricaactors

Still time to apply for our open casting for Spring Awakening! 

Off Topic are looking for creatives to join us in our new production of Frank Wedekind’s raw and revolutionary classic! We’re casting actors, looking for stage crew and other roles to join our exciting new project…if you’re interested please email offtopictheatre@hotmail.com to receive an application pack and register your place in our group workshop on 20th November 🌸

Lipa university - Liverpool - Thursday 20th November 7pm-9pm. Mount Street, Liverpool, L1 9HF

Paid on profit share basis - please note this is the play version not the musical 🎭

items.text:
**25th Anniversary Edition: International Physical Theatre Laboratory**

**December 13–22, 2025 | Schloss Laubegg, Austria**

*A transformative nine-day intensive bringing together theatre artists, dancers, choreographers, circus performers, and movement practitioners from around the world.*

The International Physical Theatre Laboratory has been a cornerstone of European physical theatre training since 2000, bringing together artists from around the world for intensive periods of artistic exchange, training, and creation. Organized by NIPAI (New International Performing Arts Institute), IPTL embodies the organization's mission to foster international collaboration and support the development of contemporary performance practices that transcend cultural and disciplinary boundaries.

Due to the intimate nature of the program and the desire to create a balanced, dynamic group, participation is limited to 15 artists. Selection is based on professional experience, artistic motivation, and the potential contribution each applicant can make to the collective laboratory experience.

**To learn more about the program, faculty, schedule, and practical details, visit: **

https://www.nipai.org/programs/international-physical-theatre-lab .
items.previewDescription: For performers and actors, dance and movement practitioners, professional artists and educators, theatre directors and stage professionals, as well as performing arts academics and students. Participants can receive a certificate upon completion.

🌸Szukamy prezenterki/tera gier telewizyjnych w nowoczesnym studiu na warszawskiej Woli! Do Twoich zadań będzie należeć prowadzenie gier karcianych transmitowanych na żywo w internetowej TV — wszystko w przyjaznym, profesjonalnym środowisku.

Szukamy osób dyspozycyjnych 5 dni w tygodniu i znających angielski min. na poziomie B1.
Oferujemy:

⭐Umowę zlecenie 
⭐ Stawkę 37,50–59 zł/h brutto + premie
⭐ Benefity: Multisport, Medicover
⭐ Pracę w trybie trzech zmian (6–14, 14–22, 22–6) + dodatek nocny 10 zł/h
⭐ Pełne, 3-tygodniowe szkolenie, dzięki któremu spokojnie wdrożysz się w obowiązki

Jeśli lubisz występować przed kamerą i chcesz pracować w dynamicznym środowisku - napisz do mnie!

🌸Szukamy prezenterki/tera gier telewizyjnych w nowoczesnym studiu na warszawskiej Woli! Do Twoich zadań będzie należeć prowadzenie gier karcianych transmitowanych na żywo w internetowej TV — wszystko w przyjaznym, profesjonalnym środowisku.

Szukamy osób dyspozycyjnych 5 dni w tygodniu i znających angielski min. na poziomie B1.
Oferujemy:

⭐Umowę zlecenie 
⭐ Stawkę 37,50–59 zł/h brutto + premie
⭐ Benefity: Multisport, Medicover
⭐ Pracę w trybie trzech zmian (6–14, 14–22, 22–6) + dodatek nocny 10 zł/h
⭐ Pełne, 3-tygodniowe szkolenie, dzięki któremu spokojnie wdrożysz się w obowiązki

Jeśli lubisz występować przed kamerą i chcesz pracować w dynamicznym środowisku - napisz do mnie!

items.text:
Versatile Musician | Singer | Guitarist — Available for Local & International Gigs 🎸

Are you looking for a versatile musician, singer, and guitarist who’s ready to perform anytime, anywhere? I’m passport-ready and available for international shows, tours, or long-term contracts abroad.

Philippines-based and available for events, bar gigs, and reliever performances from Monday to Friday — anywhere in the country!

You can reach me at:
+63 917 152 8395 (WhatsApp | WeChat | Viber | Telegram)
paulinopampy@gmail.com

Check out my performance videos on Facebook or send me a message/email if you’d like to see more materials, demos, or sample performances.

Let’s make great music together — wherever the stage takes us! 🎤🌍🎶

CASTING: 4 MODELS FOR E-COM SHOOT for half-day shoot ($400)

Tentatively set for 11/22 in DTLA. Date subject to change depending on avail.

MUST have experience and fit the sizing requirements or will not be considered. Please message me with samples of work. Looking for models with clean & elevated aesthetic for denim brand (think Revolve, AGOLDE, Levi’s)

Sizing requirements

2 women-presenting: 5’4” - 5’7”
* Waist range: 24 - 32

2 men-presenting: 5’7” - 5’-11”
* Waist range: 38 - 36

Please message me with samples of work and measurements if interested. If you don't I WILL NOT respond. Thank you!

message.text:
👉 Sei wieder dabei beim nächsten Künstler*innen Business Frühstück! ☕✨ 

🌟 Fokus: Kunst & Technologie 
 🎯 161. Künstler*innen Business Frühstück 
 📅 Dienstag, 25. November 2025 | 🕖 7:15 Uhr 
 📍 Hotel Zeitgeist Vienna, Sonnwendgasse 15, 1100 Wien 

🎤 Vortrag: Sergiu Ardelean – Gründer von Artivive 
 🗣 Moderation: Andreas Huber 

Sergiu Ardelean zeigt, wie Augmented Reality neue Wege in der Kunstvermittlung eröffnet. 
 Anhand inspirierender Beispiele wird sichtbar, wie digitale Ebenen Kunstwerke erweitern, neue Geschichten erzählen und Publikum ganz anders erreichen können. 🎨📱💡 

📲 Mehr Infos & Anmeldung: www.KünstlerBusinessFrühstück.at 
 👉 Zum Event: https://fb.me/e/aGcvE2Bju 

#künstlerinnenbusinessfrühstück #kbf #zeitgeistvienna

items.text:
How do you cope with something you never saw coming?

A short film following a couple, exploring the nuances of grief and the process of letting go.

Looking to cast Ben!

Male, 30s with a warm and comforting presence. Chemistry with Kaia is key.

Location - TBC, it will either be in Wiltshire/Hampshire or North Wales, so welcoming applications for either location.

Dates - TBC, early spring 2026, one day shooting

Compensation - unpaid, you will receive: footage, any stills, food and drink will be provided and  travel expenses paid.

This is a passion project with hopes for the festival circuit.

Please email katyelizabethcornish@gmail.com to apply, include “Ben” in the subject line, your headshot/showreel/cv or a link to Spotlight, as well as your location. 

Thank you!

A NIGHT AT THE MOVIES! ⭐️

Friday  20th of March 2026

Sub89 Reading, 

UK

We are looking for any and all movie themed acts from: 

Burlesque, Comedy, Circus, Drag, Vocalists, Magicians and all variety performers.

This is a door split show with a garaunteed minimum payment of £50.

Here at D’Lecter Cabaret diversity and inclusivity is close to our hearts and we actively encourage applications from all ages, performers of colour, LGBTQIA+, SWANA, all body types and from performers with disabilities. 

Please feel free to share this casting call with performers who may otherwise not be aware of it.

Please send your application including a video of you performing VIA EMAIL ONLY to:

Dlectercabaret@gmail.com

We are looking forward to seeing all of your Oscar worthy  submissions! 😘

Closing date for submissions is Friday 12th of December!

items.text:
Prawda boli, ale jednocześnie nas umacnia. 
Dużo siły Wszystkim po przejściach!
Tym kawałkiem udowadniam, że można iść na przód pomimo cierpienia z gwałtu, bicia i ciągłego poniżania z rąk obcego człowieka i matki, która nigdy nie zasłużyła na jej miano.
W listach do kochanka, który był w więzieniu pisała, że żałuje że mnie urodziła, że mogła mnie sobie "wyskrobać"
Posłuchaj i podaj dalej znajomym, dziś mam problemy zdrowotne przez zaniedbanie ze strony rodziców, głód i chłód.
Aktualnie jestem uziemiona w łóżku, po 2 operacjach

Schauspielerin (20, Berlin) – offen für Hauptrollen, Kurzfilme & Studentenprojekte 🎬💛

Hey zusammen 😊
ich bin Katie-Fiona Fuhrig, 20, Schauspielerin aus Berlin, und suche Rollen in Kurzfilmen, Studentenfilmen, Webserien und Independent-Projekten.

Zu mir:
• 10 Jahre Theatererfahrung
• Kameraerfahrung bei „Berlin – Tag & Nacht“
• textsicher, natürlich, zuverlässig
• flexibel & sofort verfügbar
• offen für Hauptrollen und emotionale, charakterstarke Rollen

Material:
• Portrait- & Ganzkörperfoto (schicke ich per DM)
• Vorstellungsvideo (30 Sek.)

📩 Am besten erreicht ihr mich direkt über Instagram:
👉 https://www.instagram.com/katiefuhrig

Ich freue mich sehr über Castingaufrufe & Filmprojekte in Berlin!
Liebe Grüße
Katie

items.text:
We are looking for expressive, friendly, and photogenic Berliners who are ready to be part of something innovative! Join us in front of the green screen for four hours and we'll transform you into a digital AI-avatar, to help our users explain complex topics, provide customer support, and engage with people around the world.

Send us your headshots and we’ll give you more information about this project, the casting process, and our projected filming dates later this year. 

No acting experience required. Compensation: €500. 

Contact casting@simpleshow.com to get the process started today!

–DE– 

Wir suchen ausdrucksstarke, freundliche und fotogene Berliner:innen, die Lust haben, Teil von etwas Innovativem zu werden! Komm für vier Stunden vor unseren Greenscreen und wir verwandeln dich in einen digitalen, KI-Avatar, der unseren Nutzern hilft, komplexe Themen zu erklären, Kund:innen zu unterstützen und Menschen auf der ganzen Welt zu erreichen.

Schick uns deine Headshots und wir geben dir alle weiteren Infos zu diesem Projekt, zum Casting-Prozess und zu den geplanten Drehtagen Ende dieses Monats oder Anfang Dezember.

Schauspielerfahrung ist nicht erforderlich. Vergütung: 500 €.

Kontakt casting@simpleshow.com und starte noch heute den Prozess!

We’re still looking for the right performer to play **Maria (18–23, female)** — the **antagonist** in a narrative short film exploring **girlhood, denial, and female rage** in a male-dominated world.

This is a **dance & dialogue role**, therefore we are looking for people with a more of a performance than an acting background.

We welcome **females, non-binary performers, and all ethnicities** to apply.

**Shooting:** Late January - Early February
**Auditions:** 14-15 November
**Contact:** edsh.production@gmail.com

**Darsteller (männlich, 35–45 Jahre) gesucht – Dreh am 12.12. in Freiburg & Schopfheim**

Für eine emotionale Kurzfilmproduktion suchen wir einen männlichen Darsteller im Alter von ca. **35–45 Jahren**.
Im Mittelpunkt steht die Geschichte eines Geschäftsführers, der sich zwischen beruflichem Druck und seinem Privatleben verliert – und dabei seine Familie zunehmend aus den Augen verliert.

 **Drehtermin:** 12. Dezember
 **Ort:** Freiburg & Schopfheim
 **Gage:** 150 € (Low-Budget-Produktion, Zeiten nach Absprache)

Wir suchen jemanden mit natürlicher Ausstrahlung und der Fähigkeit, Emotionen glaubhaft und authentisch rüberzubringen – keine Model- oder Schauspielschule nötig, Hauptsache echtes Spielgefühl.

Wenn du Interesse hast (oder jemanden kennst, der passen könnte), schreib gern einen Kommentar – ich melde mich dann direkt bei dir!

topComments.text: Wie passend kann eine Rolle denn auf mich zutreffen? 🙂 Gerne melden bei Interesse!

Bitte löschen, falls es nicht passt - aber es hat ja trotzdem etwas mit "Darsteller" sein zu tun und wir konnten erst letztens 3 Personen über diese Gruppe vermitteln.

+++ Darsteller als Weihnachtmann in Einkaufszentrum  +++

+++ Darstellerin als Wichtel/Engel in Einkaufszentrum  +++

WAS SUCHEN WIR:

In einem Shopping-Center im Saarland suchen wir für knapp 4 Wochen einen Darsteller als Weihnachtsmann und eine Darstellerin am Weihnachtswichtel oder Engel. Dabei betreut man eine Weihnachtsgondel und empfängt Kinder, dann natürlich auch mit dem Weihnachtsmann sprechen dürfen.

Kostüme werden gestellt

WANN: 27.11. - 24.12. (ohne die Sonntage) Unterschiedlicher Tagesaufwand zwischen 4 und 6 Stunden)

WO:  Neunkirchen (Saarland)

WAS: Betreuung einer Weihnachtsgondel als Weihnachtsmann / Wichtel

HONORAR:

- Es kommt so ein bisschen drauf an zu wieviele Termine ihr übernehmen könnt. Grundsätzlich können wir je nach Auslastung 20-25 Euro anbieten. Sollte man wirklich an allen Tagen können wäre das zw. 2500 und 3000 Euro.

- Zusätzlich kann man darüber nachdenken, ob wir euch ein Deutschlandticket für den Monat bezahlen oder evtl. ein AirBnB bezahlen.

Voraussetzungen Weihnachtsmann:

-          Alter ca. 30-60 Jahre

-          Extrovertiert, Freundlich

-          Typ "Weihnachtsmann"

Voraussetzungen Wichtel/Engel:

-          Alter ca. 20-35 Jahre

-          Extrovertiert, Freundlich

Abrechnung:

-          Am liebsten über euer Kleingewerbe

-          oder wir melden euch für den Zeitraum an

Bewerbungen & Fragen bitte an jobs@fishershouse.de

Bitte schickt uns direkt 2-3 passende Fotos von euch mit, damit wir uns einen Eindruck von euch machen können.

Schickt uns bitte außerdem die Information, an welchen Tagen ihr Zeitraum ihr verfügbar seid. Ihr müsst nicht an jedem Tag können, aber natürlich wäre möglichst häufig super :-)

Wir freuen uns auf eure Bewerbungen

items.text:
•CASTING CALL – INDEPENDENT FEATURE FILM 
Project Title: The Weight of Yesterday 
Production Type: Independent Feature Film
Shoot Dates: November 28th - 30th
Location: Denver, CO
Compensation: $500/day + Reel + IMDb Credit

SYNOPSIS:
A week before their high school’s final closure, five classmates reunite to bury a time capsule they created years ago. What begins as a nostalgic farewell quickly spirals into a raw confrontation of the truths, betrayals, and dreams that shaped their youth and the adulthood that awaits.
NOW CASTING – LEAD & SUPPORTING ROLES:

 LEAD ROLES:
Aiden (Male, 18–23)
Ambitious, witty, and fiercely protective. A natural leader haunted by a decision he made senior year that fractured the group.

Riley (Female, 18–24)
Intelligent and emotionally layered. She’s the planner of the reunion, but secretly fears what might resurface. Carries herself with quiet authority.

Lana (Female, 19–25)
Charming and impulsive with a magnetic presence. Struggles with stability and hides vulnerability behind a fearless exterior.

SUPPORTING ROLES:
Tessa (Female, 18–23)
Reserved, observant, and deeply reflective. Once the outsider of the group, she now holds crucial pieces of the past they all want to forget.

Ms. Grant (Female, 30s–40s)
A former teacher turned school counselor. Warm, insightful, and a mentor to many, but carries her own regrets about the group’s final year.

TO SUBMIT:
Email your headshot, resume, and city of residence to:
lemonlightmedias@gmail.com

Subject line: “[Your Name] – Role Submission for The Weight of Yesterday ”

topComments.text: That's not lemon light media's email address. Look up the company online. This smells scammy.
